Expose the underlying httplib::Server so consumers can mount custom routes
(e.g. devbench's REST facade) on the same host/port as the MCP transport.

Upstream keeps http_server_ private with no route hook; this adds a public
accessor. Register routes before start(). Submitted-upstream-candidate.
